Proceeds from sale of Genesys shares must be routed through a Mauritius bank 
account of Enron Distribution Ventures MHC.  This is important to maintaining 
EDV's Mauritius tax residency and therefore qualifying for exemption from 
India capital gains tax under the Indo/Mauritius Treaty.



